{"content":"    \n   <div class=\"screen \"   id=\"screen\" savrWidType=\"SCREEN\" >\n               <div class=\"rect\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"text\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        HELLO THERE\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n      \n  </div>\n    ","code":"import traceback\nasync def run_main_savr():\n    try:\n        import ginni as g\n        pgst = g.GinNode('top-progress')\n        pgst.set_visibility(False)\n        g.print('ginniPageLoadMarker8900883612800000')\n    except Exception:\n       consolelogerror(traceback.format_exc())\n\nimport asyncio\nloop = asyncio.get_event_loop()\nresult = loop.run_until_complete(run_main_savr())\n       ","css":"          .screen { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); height: 100dvh; width: 100vw;  display:inline-block;overflow-y: scroll;overflow-x: hidden; flex: 0 0 auto;position: relative;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;} \n .rect { background: rgba(209, 69, 189, 1); height: 81.93980286713828px; width: 135.38207013169017px; box-shadow: 0px 10px 20px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 6px 6px 6px 6px;position: absolute;  top: calc(50% + -104.00163194214873px);  left: calc(50% + -62.96041941656046px);} \n .text {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(241, 245, 247, 1); height: 29.287491995314326px; width: 76.23347190600407px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: